{"tid":1755784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最應該重新出發既係文宣組","createTime":"2019-11-25T18:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T11:13:23.000Z","uid":159967,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f405755e9e2df080cd948e5e732093ab6ed15494","tid":1755784,"uid":159967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:11:53.000Z","msg":"唔好理班休息/唔休息撚拗完未。<br />\n現階段一定係和理非發揮既時候，文宣要火力全開，同18區既同路人講聲唔該講聲多謝，將大圍氣氛推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d3e5588fffa41cbf3717b6bcaf3361f8155272","tid":1755784,"uid":27993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:13:14.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">手足記住 從來冇階段性勝利 我地未撚贏過</span><br />\n今次只係咁啱有區選 係支線踢走建制<br />\n亦伴隨好多負作用 出面好多分析我唔重覆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我地未贏 抗爭繼續 直到香港重光！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請保持憤怒 永遠記住俾人到谷底感覺 驕兵必敗<br />\n同時保持獨立批判思考<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtmbVr0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtmbVr0.jpg&h=6909edf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8621eb77b660c84059b1f658b3a9116daea28beb","tid":1755784,"uid":159967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef47c2bda9c7edf55790a318dbb2e49455550bca","tid":1755784,"uid":159967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla